# AI Prompt for Generating the FocusRead System

**Prompt:**

Create a **modern full-stack web application** called **FocusRead: Online Reading Assessment and Monitoring System**.

The system helps teachers assess students’ reading skills and monitor their reading progress through structured reading activities and assessments.

---

# Tech Stack

Frontend:

* TypeScript
* HTML
* CSS
* Modern responsive UI
* Clean dashboard layout
* Card-based design
* Use modern styling (Flexbox/Grid)

Backend:

* NestJS (Node.js framework)
* REST API architecture
* JWT Authentication

Database:

* PostgreSQL or MySQL

---

# User Roles

### Admin

* Manage users (teachers and students)
* Manage reading materials
* View system statistics

### Teacher

* Create reading assessments
* Upload reading passages
* Assign reading tasks
* Monitor student reading progress
* Generate performance reports

### Student

* View assigned reading tasks
* Read passages
* Take reading assessments
* View their progress

---

# Core Features

### Authentication System

* Login
* Register
* JWT authentication
* Role-based access (Admin, Teacher, Student)

### Teacher Dashboard

* View student list
* Create reading assessments
* Assign reading materials
* View reading performance

### Student Dashboard

* View assigned reading tasks
* Reading interface
* Submit answers
* View progress

### Reading Assessment System

* Teachers create reading passages
* Add comprehension questions
* Students answer questions after reading

### Progress Monitoring

* Track student reading scores
* Store assessment results
* Display charts or progress indicators

### Reporting System

* Generate reports showing:

  * reading score
  * comprehension level
  * progress over time

